{{Top|leg}}
'''Pittins''' were small creatures commonly domesticated and used as pest-catching predators in households where [[Droid/Legends|droid]] pest-removal units were impractical.<ref name="slush">{{JournalCite|14|Murder in Slushtime}}</ref> They were known for their purring,<ref name="EGTD">''[[The Essential Guide to Droids]]''</ref> and they came in a variety of [[Color/Legends|colors]].

The original homeworld of the pittin was unknown, though they were tamed on many [[Planet/Legends|worlds]], including [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan]]. [[Tia Organa]] kept pittins as pets, four in all; they were named [[Taffy]], [[Winkie]], [[Fluffy (pittin)|Fluffy]], and "[[All-Terrain Attack Vehicle]]," the last named by [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]]. These pittins were presumed dead in the [[Destruction of Alderaan/Legends|destruction of Alderaan]].

Pittins were also found on [[Belsavis/Legends|Belsavis]] where they were known to eat amphibians and [[myrmin]]s.

